07/03/85  executive_mail, xmail

Syntax:  xmail


Function:  invokes the Executive Mail facility.


Notes:
To invoke the Executive Mail facility, type either "executive_mail" or
"xmail" when a ready message (usually of the form "r 14:03 0.285 5")
appears on the terminal screen just above the cursor.  User requests
are made by selecting operations from menus (or lists).  All help
needed to operate the system is available within the Executive Mail
facility itself.


The -multics_mode (-mm) control argument is OBSOLETE.  Refer to the
Multics Command Mode option in the Personalize Executive Mail menu.
